### Test shortage prediction via Express proxy (port 5000)
### Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT from login.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Predict shortage risk
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ml/predict-shortage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendance_percentage": 72.5,
  "absent_days": 12
}

###

### Invalid input (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ml/predict-shortage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendance_percentage": 150,
  "absent_days": -1
}

###

### Direct Flask (bypass Express) — port 8000
# POST http://localhost:8000/predict
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "attendance_percentage": 72.5, "absent_days": 12 }
